The '''First Bodyguard''' was the title of the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] leader of the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[Bodyguard/Legends|bodyguard]]. Before the [[Showdown on Coruscant|Jedi Rebellion]] and the replacement of the Jedi by the Knights of the [[Sith/Legends|Sith]], the First Bodyguard was [[Kane Starkiller]].

==Behind the scenes==
In the first draft, Kane is renamed Akira Valor. He remains the same character, however, in all other respects.

The notion of the Jedi being Imperial bodyguards may have inspired the [[Imperial Knight]]s in the [[Star Wars: Legacy]] series.

